headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: Ocelot Jugular
content: Saunter over to the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort and give the Lucky Wheel a spin to win GTA$, RP, clothing, snacks, and all sorts of mystery prizes to boot. This week’s top prize on the podium is none other than the Ocelot Jugular — a prim and proper sports saloon that hides a freakish engine under its bonnet.
